Jason Willinger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_Willinger 0 Jason Willinger (born 1971) is an American actor and voice actor, who is best known for providing the voice of Robbie Sinclair in the television sitcom Dinosaurs. He also provided additional voices for the film A Goofy Movie.Willinger has also co-starred in the 1992 film Zebrahead and guest-starred in the television sitcoms Cybill and Champs. In 2006, Willinger was the narrator for the reality television series Everest: Beyond the Limit and in Cesar 911.
